You can remove the payment type after but you have to do this manually after each transaction. it's a pain. I remove the payment method and change my password at the same time. Great otherwise.

For cheap products? Yes, this app is good. I've been using this app since december. At first, i'm very satisfied with the minimum purchase order. But lately, I noticed it that everytime you purchased specially if you do order like 2x a week, the minimum purchase increases. Which really frustrating at the moment (minus star for that). Another thing, your free item game (fishland and farmland) another minus stars for each. This game takes you forever to win the free items. Sucks!
replyContent: Hello, thank you for participating in our promotional activities and we are sorry that you are experiencing difficulties with your rewards. Customer satisfaction is of the utmost importance and we are constantly working to improve our service quality. For any help, please contact us through Temu.com or Temu app live chat. Best wishes, Temu Team

content: So many cheap and reasonable products to buy. But there is ONLY 1x issue that I have, is most of the clothing isn't the exact colours as the picture, and the fabric isn't the exact quality as seen in the photo. Very disapointed with that, because the photos has very good quality to them, and i've bought certain clothing, and was made out of cheap and nasty fabric and colours that dnt really look like the photo. I haven't sent any of the items back, because it would cost me even more for return

I deleted the app because I had a bad experience: my order was not delivered at all due to issues with the carrier, as they claimed. Whenever I raise a complaint or enquire on my order status, they would come up by offering credit for the delay. Reordering the same item and having to wait again is unacceptable. Even after waiting, there's no guarantee it will be delivered.

Aggressively targets you with offer notifications. I had to uninstall the app because of this as it was way too much. As for the quality of the products, it's a mixed bag really but it's very cheap. Also be careful about the in app offers. Some make it look like you'll get a free $100 offer with just a few purchases but in reality you need to spend hundreds to earn the coins needed. It's a shame they have to resort to shady sales tactics as it isn't that bad without them.

Garbage. They have games for "free items," which are meh. That are impossible to complete without spending 1000's of dollars. And if you return the stuff thats not as described, they punish you for it & take more currency than it was worth. It's misleading at the best of times and support is meh. Also, I'd definitely compare prices to Amazon before purchasing here. Some are definitely better, and some are definitely worse.

I love shopping at Temu, 98% of the items I've purchased have been well made and definitely worth the money. The games on the other hand, are very annoying. You have to keep sharing/ inviting people and ordering stuff to get rewards that are supposed to help you get free items. We don't all know hundreds of people to share/invite and can only do that do much before they get annoyed. They amount of $ I spend ordering so I can claim free stuff, I may as well just buy it .

I really did enjoy shopping on here, but I can no longer add or remove things from my wishlist and it's very irritating. Would be a 4-5 star without this problem. If this gets fixed I will change my review, I've updated the app, uninstalled and reinstalled, doesn't change. Rewrite- issue fixed and everything working well now. I've missed a few items in my orders but get a refund with store credit within a few hours. Good app.

App gives no problems, it's just a bit difficult to search through your wishlist. I would love to be able to sort my wishlist into boards or categories as on other online shopping apps. Also being able to manage wishlist items as you can your cart, to be able to selected more than one at a time to remove them for example would save a lot of time!

Where do I even start...Ordered few items 4 weeks ago. It had only been packaged 10 days after & even then all the items I bought weren't available(despite purchasing the "last one").I was urged to pay tax(which I did)& expected it to be delivered two weeks after order..still not here. Wrote to support team for tracking assistance, they weren't much help. My issue is that I could've used different platforms to buy items instead. Disappointed but a learning curve. Temu has potential but serviceüëé

Cons: Items not always as ad descriptions and pics. With clothing, a TV investigation proved that pics are of high end clothes but the items sold are cheap, poor quality copies. I agree with others that games to get free gifts are rigged and impossible to achieve, and the constant pop ups from the app is enough to want to cancel. Pros: Free shipping (for a minimum spend) and returns, no problem with refunds, sometimes while keeping the item if cheaper than the cost to Temu of return shipping.

This Is a total scam. I don't know how is it possible that they are allowing this here. 1. It ads for an item with x price and when you go to buy it, it jumps like 2x the original. 2. The reviews on the app are controlled by the app. They allow only best reviews on. 3. There are some games on the app which is impossible to complete. 4. It says for an item that it has 90% off, but when you go there and see from the original price, not even it doesn't have any change but it's increased.

content: I really like the app, but: it keeps asking me everytime to allow notifications, which is very annoying. And all the sales are fake, the price you see is the normal price. You get what you pay for so dont expect high quality products, but most things are at least usable. I have bought so much stuff.. some of the things are very cool and appreciated things, some was given away or trashed. It's a bit hit or miss, make sure to read the descriptions and reviews. Deliveries went all perfectly.

Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. I've been accessing this about 2 years and never had any mix-up. Until yesterday it kept hanging for no reason. My phone is totally up to date. Also the app is up to date. I've tried deleting and reinstalling it mutiple times, checked my internet connection, restarting my phone, and I still have enough memory, and tried other phones. It's just my phone that does it. But it only happens when the loading screen is done. The login screen is fine though.

It is a very good app to buy things you can not get in the stores. It is a hit or miss with items when you get them. The many problems I have with it is the limited time offer like Hat trick, you choose free items and you have to get the energy bar to 100% by sharing and having app user click on a link, you only have 24 hours to get it done with might end up losing them all. The programmers need to change that let the owners let user used their store credits to pay the difference.

Pros: Great app, similar to Aliexpress but with less fake products (it still does have fake products), far fewer duplicate sellers, and with faster delivery times and better delivery pricing, specials are amazing. Cons: Search algorithm could be a little better (minor fault), product range is far less than the likes of the other major online shops.

content: When this first came out, it was pretty amazing. Good deals, discounts, vouchers. Now there is no longer vouchers and things seem to be getting closer to retail price. -1 star for those. -1 for the fact that the wish list only holds 300 items plus no way to sort them/view by price/discount etc. I think it would be great to up the amount, add the sort, or at least add an option to sort items into sub-groups/smaller lists. Edited to remove another star because there is now a $45 minimum purchase.

content: Great selection. Constant bombardment of emails and I would imagine notifications but I disabled those as the start. Lots of promos that you never seem to actually get. Good products at really good prices. Taking 10 days or so for the shipments to come. If you can pick and choose wisely you can get some really obscure specialty type items at really good prices. Definitely an interesting find. But like most companies, they only want a steady stream of your money.

content: It does okay with providing plenty of cheap options for items. Large variety with free shipping. The downside is getting bombarded with "deals" and cheap items that are on sale. The vast majority of these items are trash, and they're just trying to flog them off to people however they can. I'm getting sick of all these "deal" notifications, and the coupons which are offered only as part of large bundles of coupons. Gotta give it to the Chinese, they do try. But I think I've had enough of Temu.

Okay, some great prices, some nice stuff some I haven't seen before. But you need to pick the right time for 1st order otherwise you don't get any freebie for your 1st order, but you get a load of messages advertising one then get told its for new customers. Most offers are only cheap in 1/2 colours (not the nice reds and blues etc). Clothes are all small, a XL is marked as being size 16. Be carefull some offers or vouchers aren't what you think they are. I Can't find my saved products.

Ok anything that is free is straight up a scam. You'll spend months trying to get these free items where they'll ask you to essentially share the app so more people download the app. Unfortunately this is never ending and 'closer' you are to finishing and attaining the 'free gift', they reduce the rewards exponentially to make it unattainable. As for actually buying, it's the same as AliExpress, just seems to be faster, AliExpress has picked up on this and has started shipping faster too.

content: THEY JUST DON'T STOP SPAMMING YOU I got the app and brought some things, yes they are slightly cheaper, the email updates & shipment, how quick they were was so good. But the sad thing that lets them down is, you get maybe 10 emails a day about offers and texts as well. They start at 8am and just don't stop. I have never had a company message me so much, it is disappointing & makes the shipping, service go from great, to me getting rid of the app & blocking the emails. I know of others similar.

content: Communication once order is placed borders on excessive. Far too many promotional messages which become irritating and time wasting. Prices very low and on occasions quality may not quite meet expectations as a result. Excellent handling of returns. I like the idea of my account being credited immediately (an excellent marketing idea because I am immediately tempted to place a new order.Product sizing pretty accurate compared with UK sizes, maybe they are slightly on the larger size.

Ordered a fair bit off temu now and only had one disappointment at this stage ( probably my fault for not reading the description properly) but everything else has exceeded my expectations. Quality and price are exceptional. Delivery takes around 10 days and again, I have not been let down. The only downside to shopping on temu is finding the right key words for the style of thing you're after, for instance, searching something like 'vintage' accesses the more handcrafted, decorative items.

Only the first shopping is a good experience and the delivery is fast. Every time you order, the delivery time gets longer and longer. Prices are not cheap anymore. Most of the products, especially dresses and clothes, you can buy better quality from some actual brands for the same price or even cheaper. You shop more, and the prices on the app get higher for you because they think they got you! It is worth only 1 time shopping.

The app itself is good. Order worked well and delivery was very good and quick. My problem however is the methods the app uses to give discounts but then all of a sudden items are "sold out" until you enter normally, then its there again to order. Sales gimmicks i dont appreciate. If you skip and ignore the gimmicks and just order what you want, then it works well.

the best service I have ever experienced! was a problem with the courier company and they refunded me my entire delivery. the other deliveries I have received In 2 weeks, of course I would want my purchases on time but it's good to know they took my complaint seriously. the items are really value for money and I can always find exactly what I am looking for. I love all the rewards and discounts as I would of bought the items anyways but then I feel its value for money and I can get more stuff..

I reside in South Africa, and my 1st order came through on the specified date indicated. ALL goods were tested, and in working order. The Temu app is easy to use and navigate through. There is also an option to reduce the price further if you check your order and see if the same Item(s) have dropped in price, credit is applied to your app wallet in less that 2 seconds.

Love it, mostly, their policies on returns and refunds are great, no hassle at all. Some of the descriptions are a wee bit misleading and you have to click on every option to get to the advertised price; colours and sizes may be different prices. Also they have a tendency to reward new customers far better than loyal customers, the amount you have to spend to get free delivery went up from ¬£10 to ¬£15. But the quality of most stuff is great so overall worth it.

NZ CUSTOMERS: Took 2+ weeks for delivery. Even though I live in Auckland not far from the airport. Items didn't arrive at all, over $400 worth over 3parcels. Company was happy to refund the under $20 parcels but not the rest. Even though I ordered everything together, somehow it got split into 3. its been 3 weeks trying to get refunded. No contact number and emails are very very slow. FAST HORSE EXPRESS is who they use and are absolutely useless. Also no way to contact delivery service.

What a major scam. Someone invited me to get free gifts. When I downloaded and joined the app. I got 100 free items. The as I was choosing items I got to the 10th item. Got ready to check out and the screen refreshed. Next thing I knew. I no longer was able to choose anything for "free". Oh and it's not for free. It's only free on the condition that buy some items as well. Which they also don't tell you. If I could 0 give stars. I would. 0/10. I DON'T RECOMMEND ANYONE WASTING THEIR TIME.

content: I was a bit skeptical about this. I placed my order for a watch.seeing that it's the first time using this app, I made small purchase just as a test. And to my surprise, it was delivered in front of my house.its good because I can track each every step from purchase up to delivery. The only thing that caught off guard was the duty tax,but it's understandable to pay that fee for items to come into the country. I'll definitely purchase from Temu again.

The items are cheap quality, although the photos look very attractive on the app. The packaging is not practical. They put all my purchased items almost 40 items in one nylon bag, without any protection. Many items were damaged and most of the items were opened!!! I don't prefer to deal with Temu any more. All other websites are providing safety packaging, good quality and competitive prices.

Have had no issues with this app. The products have been of good quality, and the delivery time has been better than similar apps. I appreciate that the size charts reflect the sizes in my country and that they have been fairly accurate. The only problem is with the games for free gifts. For us older people who do not have hundreds of online friends, we aren't able to send out the required invites to ever get the free gifts.

I never had any problem with Temu. The shipping is always free. BUT you need to be aware that the choice is limited in the number of products available contrary to AliExpress, AND you already need to know well what you want to buy. I never bought any clothes, so, I was never disappointed. As usual with this company, you need to compare. Sometimes for exactly the same product, AliExpress is cheaper (especially on objects made of titanium). But anyway, I recommend it.

I've always been a bit skeptical with apps full of "cheap price" or "great deals". However, after receiving my first order I can confirm this app is legitimately good with all the items they provide and the price they offer. The popups may be a bit annoying and the shipping does take a week but heck with the value of the product they offer there's nothing else I can complain about.

Keeps saying free shipping on all orders try to check out, says min. 35$ to check out.The prices: if you search something in a specific price range, it will show the cheapest item's price on the item that you want but when you actually click on the one you wantsuddenly the price goes up.NO wishlist. All games say"free gifts, redeem all" and then they push to invite people. STRAIGHTSHIP IS THE WORST SHIPPING COMPANY, LOST 2 PACKAGES.

As an AliExpress Veteran, it was a tough choice to make to use Temu. Prices not differ much, the advantage of Temu is that shipping is generally faster. I got everything I ordered without problems, got good discounts and even a free studio light as part of a promotion. The constant harassment through mail, sms and anything they can get a hold of with fake deals and discounts is annoying and the search bar is useless. Unless it's a very common thing you're looking for, you're doomed.

The first time I got a good price. The second time, they gave me spin coupons to buy more and more, which felt like a trap. I uninstalled it by mistake. The third time, they changed the prices of the whole app for the reinstallation process. The fourth time I bought, but the coupon didn't work for me. It was a really bad experience. I suggest to you using another platform.
replyContent: Salve Saeedur, grazie per averci contattato e ci scusiamo per eventuali disagi. Se hai ulteriori domande, non esitare a contattarci tramite Temu.com o la live chat dell'app. Siamo qui per aiutarti a trovare una soluzione. Grazie!

content: The app seems sketchy but it's true when they say don't judge a book by its cover. Things are cheap and you can access a wide range of quality material. Electronics, cosmetics, fashion trends and all that. This is a brilliant app. If you looking to start a business just link yourself up with this marvelous app. Although I hate waiting. But I have no complains about the products and the services.

Overall I am quite happy with this app. Sometimes the products dont come as expected, but its easy to make a refund. I really like those many options and the cheap prizes. Some local products at my place, which would be comparable are not even affordable. I hope that the people producing these products are well payed, but I can not proof how the conditions are. Be careful with the reviews! Sometimes they are fake. And always look for pictures in the ratings.

I gave it four stars because when they package a large order with items of varying shapes and sizes, things are crushed in to fit in the bag. Sometimes, things are so crushed that it makes the item break or have a crack. Also, many packages arrive with holes in the bag, and merchandise is sticking out. Other than that, I am satisfied with almost everything. The prices and quality of the items are very good.

Most of the items are as described. The cloths not so much. Make sure you read the description it tells you what it's really made of. 90% of their cloths are polyester, and a lot of the footwear isn't really as described or what the pic shows. A huge problem are returns, you don't get your money back you may get half the money & who knows where the other half goes. The price you see when ordering is always higher on the reciept.

Some items are of cheap material, others not. Its a decent app. What I hate about this app is the free item section where it just gets impossible to complete unless you invite people who have never used temu before which is really hard. I love the fact you have to earn it but hate that it gets nearly impossible. Earn 1 penny for every person you invite that accepts it when you need $2 worth left to get anything. Impossible

The app works great. The 1st order was delivered on time. The ordering and payment gateway, etc, all works perfectly, as per local payment gateways, like Ozow. Good products if chosen well. But, South African courier partners can be a problem (as is usually the case with most things South African). Nevertheless, all orders arrived, and where there was a delay, their usual R20.00 credits were applied. Don't panic on delays. As they can happen. Best to contact their customer service with delays.

I've ordered quite a few times Always read the description and look at the pictures for measurements, as you could end up with a miniature version of what you wanted. If it doesn't have measurements, it's best to look at other similar items. I find the prices are really good. However, if it's really cheap, you'll probably find the item is not made well. Go up a price bracket. You also get the difference back if the item you purchased drops in price within 30 days of your purchase.

I've been very happy with most items. The dresses are particularly good, easy care and fit well. If anything is not right, Temu has refunded very promptly. Very good prices. I do have concerns about the 'free' shipping. last time I had to spend $55 for 'free' shipping. Before that, items were all free shipping. Also not keen on the fishland games where the goal posts keep changing and seemingly the only way to get an item for 'free' is to coerce others to sign up or spend $$$ of dollars.

Great app. Works well as I haven't found any issues other than while paying duty taxes through the third party. It still worked, just that that process wasn't as seamless... The app updated delivery status an hour after receiving my order which is no big deal really but just thought to include that bit of info if useful to users or developers. But otherwise great variety of products, well priced, and timely delivery guarantee.

At first, I was a little unsure how to navigate, but very soon, no problems at all. Just don't like the promotion games, if you don't have lots of people contacts, you can't get FREE items. I have purchased many items and only received 3 for free, the first time using TEMU. I believe that my Loyalty should qualify me automatically for FREE ITEMS of MY CHOICE, when I place an ORDER. Delivery service is ok, but waiting more than 3 days for packages is too long.

I love this app. Contrary to reviews I've read, I have had no problem with shipping, and I've placed 6 orders. It's easy to use and so far the quality of goods I've received is excellent. The app is not glitchy and doesn't lag, at least not on my phone. Enjoy! Edit: I'm in my 15th order and I've had zero issues. Nothing has been late and nothing has been hacked/stolen/etc. I'll keep shopping. What's sad though is that none of these items would be affordable if made here in the US.

Notifications are a bit of an overkill, one a day would by fine (I'd actually like that) but it feels like one every hour, if you link your email and phone number, that increases the notifications too. Tbh, I expected as much. Otherwise I'm impressed. I've only ordered one shipment so far, the items were good quality and it arrived in reasonable time. I plan to buy more soon.

This app is good so far, there are good deals! What REALLY annoys me though is that when I try to buy things that are 7 dollars or something less than 10 dollars, it won't let me buy it at all. It always wants me to add even more things to my cart, when I don't need anything else. This just doesn't seem necessary at all, why not just let me/us buy what we want without having to add anything extra to our cart? This is just ridiculous to me.

bombards you with garbage, you can't find items by searching, even if you copy a listing headline verbatim it will not show up until you scroll through many related searches because they want to sell more rather than let you find what you need and leave. The games are dumb but I figured out how to win free stuff without actually sharing or inviting people so that's cool. It's shady and no wonder people are so addicted. Be cautious, limit your time, and manage your expectations.

There are lots of goodies for a bargain. Delivery was always on time. The items I bought all came in great condition and new. Refunded items were quick , and after the purchases, you are allowed to price adjustments for any lowered price change on items. Overall, I had a great experience shopping with Teemu, and yes, I would recommend everyone to shop here.

Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. It's best shopping app, simple yet good and it doesn't get old with the amount of decks. Each item is different compared to the next. The over leveled issue is only on ladder, and that isn't too bad. You can beat other with higher level cards if you are good. Nice animations and graphics. The events are fun for people who don't have everything yet. A nice and refreshing game for those that enjoy a strategy game. Things get balanced often, get this game.

Peace, very much too much advertisements sent, had to discontinue for found no way to greatly reduce amount of advertisements sent. If it was not for the one item I sent for came back wrong, the many other items I have purchased over time, am happy to of obtained them. That's why I am not giving a 5 star rating, but would of till that very important item came back not what I asked for. Must of been a glitch in computer system, for I was very careful in what I asked for.

Awesome app. Yeah they have heaps of emails and notifications. It's pretty simple. Turn those off in your settings and you won't receive them ü§£ Look at peoples reviews and pictures before buying an item. I am happy with every single product I have brought. I have won even more for free ü§£ the free gift games to win prizes aren't a scam. You definitely can win 10 items for free. You just have to know how to play the game properly. Can't expect them to make it easy to win free stuff. Takes work

The app itself is fine. It's the question of quality of the products they sell that can be poor. I have ordered an oximeter that lit up, but never operated. A couple solar powered cars never worked, thin blankets. Guitar picks were flimsy. But some stuff was great. A lot of their figurines/knick knacks were very nice. I bought a blanket that blew me away with it's quality, so did a couple of metal spinners I got to help with my anxiety. The kalimbas are decent too

I have been shopping with Temu for over a few years now. I have never had any issues with deliveries or items never sent. So far, i have never had any issues with the quality of their products. When you have an issue with any item from your order, they resolve our issues right away with just a few clicks and photos showing the issues with your product. That's one of the things I love about THE MOST OF TEMU returns. policies make me feel secure when placing orders.

I am actually extremely disappointed as of today. I love the selection & variety, and *DID* like the promo opportunities with referrals. HOWEEVER, after failing to get even close on those, I stopped trying. Then I was invited into another, that was awesome! it had a 24hr timer from start and I more than double the referral acceptances it implied would be needed. I have potentially made them $100,000.00 plus from it. and they continued to add more and more requirements. you can't win.

content: Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. Awesome! I have been shopping from temu app for 3 years but the feeling I used to get earlier is not available recently. We request you not to spoil the temu app again.

Bad experience with temu, you always see 50% off for first time users, but when checking out it doesn't discount it, gives you a coupon for 10 free gifts but upon checking out they impose almost impossible condition of inviting so many others,but they also need to accept the invite and install the app and it is not only one, it will be 2 then , another person, so effectively it is waste of time. Products look cheap but when clicking thru even price changes. Same item and price keeps changing.

far too many advertisement emails. keep swomping my inbox with offers that are all the same but aren't what they first appeared. Order's get split up and can be hard to track. if you do take advantage of the 100% cash back deal it is money off vouchers! do NOT opt in to text alerts for the same reason absolutely swomping me with texts. most of the goods are good/reasonable quality, Avoid electronics as in my experience none of the items I purchased have worked. ALWAYS READ DISCRIPTION

content: Minimum spend starts nicely at $15, then as you become a regular shopper it jumps up significantly to $35., now it's $40 Is it really worth it? Also, it doesn't let you review items honestly with accurate photos and videos. I am always having to edit my reviews to get it posted. Prices are good though and transactions are easy with fast deliveries.

It was ok to begin with. However. The "100% back in vouchers" deal is a total fiddle, and the minimum spend keeps going up. And I keep hearing horror stories about bank fraud, but have yet to see anything substantiated. They were quick to refund the wireless earbuds that were rubbish, oddly enough didn't want them back. They've gone for recycling. So long, Temu, and thanks for all the fish

I've been testing this app, and while it shows promise, I believe it could greatly benefit from the addition of a wishlist or favorites feature. It's not immediately clear how to star an item I enjoyed, which detracts from the overall user experience. Incorporating a wishlist function would not only make it easier for users to save and revisit items they love but also enhance engagement and satisfaction with the app. I'm eagerly üíñ

this place has great deals. but some items could be made a little better. And some things are going. fairly decent delivery time. plus good they give you a chance at other deals and discount's. Some of their prices are a little high on some of their stuff and sometimes you will get some stuff that comes in damaged. Love shopping on Temu, great stuff for cheaper prices, it's not junk that is sold. The products hold up excellent. Intrusive app. Too many pop-ups, fake promos and the "free gifts" you're supposed to get following app activities are impossible to get due to changing goal posts. It's a bit of a swizz. Good for cheap items, but you get what you pay for.

Great items if you pick the right ones,I had several large delivery's,most things usable in some way.some items,NOT worth buying, has eu/Asia plugs ect.I have assortment of fishing tackle thats great,several bags which also great.small crafting item,been ideal,some larger rulers where spot on! material is bit hit & and miss,but some bargains to be had. if you need something quick, don't wait for these as it's a good 6 to 7 days wait. so far great stuff and great price!

they constantly bug with fake free gifts & free $$ so u turn off notifications& then they bug you to turn notifications back on. you can't ever just open the app & buy what you need without some type of harassing pop ups enticing you to purchase more or play some ridiculous game. if you play along they offer you items at a higher price as if you're saving $$ but the same item can be found for less if you search for it yourself on their app. shipping takes a long time always.

So far so good. I love the app... Only one thing I would love... Make it easier to add to your favorites. Temu, it says shop like a billionaire.. it means get ready to spend spend spend. So much stuff you didn't even know you needed until you see it for the price..2nd mortgage taken out already, credit cards loaded... addictive spending... as with all cheaper products, some pretty below average, BUT, TEMU refund & returning is easy if required at all. Temu are very fair & customer satisfaction orientated but the coupon system is confusing & in place to make you spend more.. constant reminders annoy!

repeatedly have not had items in the package. They want you to take pictures of the package to make sure if it's not damaged, if it's damaged it somehow your fault. did not get free gift in last package, can't even ask for it to be replaced because you can't select the item to request them to send it again. many items don't work or break immediately. replyContent: Hello, thank you for reaching out. Customer satisfaction is of the utmost importance and we are constantly working to improve our service quality. content: I have purchased a lot of items on Temu and the majority of things I have ordered are very nice and the material of the clothing is very comfortable. I particularly liked the black pull on butterfly pants and short sleeve vneck top to match. I bought navy butterfly pants as well because I love the rhinestone butterflies on them. I love my anchor top with the vneck and matching Capri pants and I bought jeans with a big bow on the back bottom part and little rhinestones across the bottom also.

I was sceptical about using this app and even more sceptical about what I might receive. However, the app is simple to use, service is amazing! Make sure you customise the communications to suit your needs otherwise you will be bombarded! Also, when you see something you like, search the app for similar items as prices vary! All in all, a great app!

%99 of clothing is true to size, some clothing is a tiny bit small and some are a little bit big. lip gloss is perfect for under $2. some items need an easier way like an assembly panflet to put together the item. cause some items are like science experiments. very happy with everything and won't return anything.

The goods are reasonably priced right across the board. Long time to arrive, but worth it. Lots of useful little devices to help arounqqd the house. Clothes not so impressive and sizes confusing sometimes. Clothes often notbtailored and fabrics not of good quality. Lots of quirky bits and pieces not found in UK. Lots if cheap little toys too. many items cheaper than Amazon and exactly the same. Remu keep you well informed of delivery time and you can easily update yourself. Returns easy.

prices are great. most items true to size, hand bags are only thing been disappointed with. when you see an item keep looking as you may find same item cheaper. you do get credit if late. refunds are easy if you are honest and review items regular items can take up to 2 weeks to come all in all very happy

disappointment and frustration regarding my recent experience with your online platform. This is the second time I have encountered a major issue with my order, which was delivered to the wrong address, resulting in a significant delay in receiving my purchase. I understand that mistakes can happen occasionally, but it is essential for a reputable online platform to take responsibility and rectify these issues promptly and efficiently.

i like it. you can find many things that are not available anywhere else. where it is available elsewhere, temu is mostly less. none of my orders has gone more than 7 days order to deliver. temu's price match process is completely automated and can be used to scan orders for lower prices up to 30 days. the games are impossible to win unless you place orders (caution suggested). wish it was easier to bring friends to temu. I know how I felt before I tried it, so I don't blame them.

Never in doubt, the prices, and items I bought aready, great value for the dollar. great, awesome, app. reminds me of wish, unfortunately I was kinda addicted, but told about this one, and im not gonna lie, I catch my down time, scrolling though this app. but the quality and price too great. trying to save money seems impossible when I'm able to get great deals. the shipping way better on temu compared to wish, that's for sure.

Amazing range of products @ unbelievable prices. A few words of advice - if you see something you like put it straight in your cart because sometimes going back to find it again can be a very time consuming process - there's just so much to look at & you'll keep getting distracted. Duplicates @ different prices you can remove from your cart later. ENJOY!

Very good selections and prices. Delivery was much faster then aliexpress. The "promotions" are very annoying and low value. I have spent 100s of dollars and played fishland for months with no chance of getting my prizes. 99.97 stuck forever. The last 2 fish require 100 percent at 0.01 per feeding of 10 grams per. This is 100,000 grams food and just 10 seconds waiting per is 10000 times 20 seconds or 56 hours to just input if you had 100000 grams I am leaving to the cheaper aliexpress.

They have the most shameless, scammy, misleading, promotion stuff that‚Äôs obviously ridiculous. I don‚Äôt know, maybe it‚Äôs legit in some dimension and technically isn‚Äôt a scam, but it‚Äôs definitely ridiculous. You just X out of it, and it‚Äôs cool. The app itself is legit; there are great deals. It‚Äôs like Amazon‚Äôs plug. Shipping to the US is often done in about a week. Basically the same as Ali. Slightly different mostly the same. I have purchased quite a lot of off Temu. I am more than happy with most purchases, one item arrived broken, I filled in the returns form & sent photos as requested the cost of it was repayed in minutes. The other item was not the correct sizes, again went through the returns form, cost was credited to my account & told to keep the items. I can't fault Temu

Like most apps, it goes downhill with updates. It was a better app when I could just shop without having to navigate through a bunch of spinning wheels that say I can get free stuff, because that is just a LIE. I have no patience for companies that LIE to me. I'm not shopping temu much anymore these days. Amazon is more expensive, but they don't lie to me about fake savings.

They show you alot of stuff you already bought. Their credit back now sucks. Used to be you could do multiples and get it when they ship the order. Now they make you go in everyday to get it split in 6 days and u lose it if you dont come back each day. But you can only use it once per day and 2 times until u claim the credits. Why cant i find certain shoes in size 12. Ive been looking for months across many sellers.

There's a wide variety of quality items here & if something is wrong, they promptly will make it right! They also have many unique items, & you can find most anything you're looking for. They do make it hard to leave their site with pop ups. So far, that's the only drawback.

The merchandise on this site is great. The only thing I don't like is alot of the material is that silky stuff when it should be cotton or spandex. It's misleading especially the women sweatsuits. The girls plaid skirts an cardigan sweaters are extremely nice. But overall I really like this site. The prices are great. Sometimes, the delivery is annoying an delayed. Will continue to be my go to shopping site. Thanks Temu.

Compared to other websites like Aliexpress, got to shop round for similar deals as to the same thing, as both like Temu offer you some great stuff to buy and cheaper than shopping in your local town and city centre. but only thing is that you have to spend min of ¬£15 on ever order and still can spend less than ¬£15, if you want to add for to your latest order before shipping out.

I haven't used the coupons because you have to shop to get the coupons. I think the 20.00 minimum order isnt right.

Its like Amazon. Temu offers free shipping for the most part unless purchasing product from local warehouse under 30 dollars(I stay away from it). Your experience is based on your research. It's important to specify the type of product such material if your looking for clothes. For instance Cotton or spandex ect. And ratings is a must and I stand to a standard such as no less than 4.7 and read negative. Great prices and quality. And temu will refund bad product & accommodate 4 late shipping

I was skeptical about ordering off of temu. Their clothes options were in my style range which I haven't been able to find in a while. So, I took a stab and ordered. (didn't fit my large chest) the return process seems easy. take to the UPS print your QR code and off it goes. I will be ordering more from TEMU. üëçüëç

a lot of the things are really good quality and you can definitely pick up a bargain or two if you shop shavvy that is. amazing so happy. exactly as picture, good quality. sizing was perfect, not too small and not to big. won't slip if your skinny for the size,and space to grow or make some good use out of it for a season or 2 without worrying to size up too soon. obviously some threads flying about but that's not a problem, just trim with some scissors, survived a good machine wash, colour still perfect, fabric still perfect and not shrinkage or misshapen no colour run either. if you zoom on the advertised photo

content: Most items of clothing are BREATHTAKINGLY beautiful and well worth the money. Initially TEMU made me very happy! Nevertheless, approximately 20% of items were faulty, wrong, or not delivered. Because I can not print return labels and are unable to reach the post office, I can not return these items for refund. I also can not see a link to report missing items. For me that translates to a loss of 20%. Therefore, after purchasing over 350 items, I decided TO STOP PURCHASING FROM TEMU!

Returns are a a pain! I ordered a splint for a sprained ankle and after following their size chart, it arrived way too big. I wanted to exchange it, and they wanted me to take it to the post office to return it. I can't walk or drive to the post office (it's my right foot - the foot used for driving.) I'm just going to end up going to Walmart or Amazon or something. It may be more expensive but I'm not going to risk them sending me the wrong size again and waiting weeks to get it.

I have liked most things I have purchased and I will keep purchasing as I fund the quality is good and so is the choice. I have only had one broken item and the value of it was refunded with no issue. I think you need to look at sizes as some pictures can be deceptive but they always have measurements so really need to check those and not rely on pictures. overall very good shopping experience.

Have ordered twice with no problems, everything went smoothly and their products are very affordable. I did keep receiving ads in notifications but you can stop this by going into Temu's settings, you have many choices under your control by pressing the Edit buttons there.

I've bought plenty from this app, and I'm satisfied with most of what I get. But as for winning from any of the pick "X" amount of items games, forget I get any where from 10 cents to 1 cent away from winning, and then suddenly anyone accepting invites is invalid. Forget finding a "new" user. They come up invalid, too

The pros are the variety of items that Temu has which is vast. Most prices are Great UNLESS they have " specials " where the "original " price is way higher than normal .

I have ordered many items from Temu and will probably continue to do so. The items are always well packaged, arrive within expected delivery dates and any missing, damaged or ill fitting items are immediately replaced. Contact with customer services is easy, however I do have one issue. These bonus /money back/refund schemes. I'm unsure if they are genuine. I always seem to get them AFTER an order. The phone app is perfect. I mainly buy art supplies from Temu because the quality is incredible. Overnight shipping isn't that important to me, so waiting 4-5 days isn't a problem. I've made over a dozen orders this year and had a problem with only one or two items. When I notified Temu, they issued a prompt credit.

This review comes after I've been a returning customer for some time now. I've spent over $600 since I joined and everything I have ordered has arrived in perfect condition. Each item has performed as advertised. Temu can be as infectious as gambling, though. I find it difficult to stop buying things because I'm always finding something I "just gotta have". Go ahead and download the app, make an account, and have fun finding those "must haves" you just can't live without!

Temu. I was a little addicted. There are some hits and a few misses. Good cleaning products. A lot of the household items are for minimal living and therefore may not hold a lot of weight. Clothing,some fantastic items and some strange items . A lot of polyester garments check reviews they help immensely. I like seeing pictures from real people. Easy return options I find it convenient. just watch your spending as you can get carried away

I just received first order. Came on time, was just ser on ground next to door. Outer packaging was taped several places where plastic packaging had been ripped. I ordered canvas with saying on it, corners were ripped, so now I have to go shopping for another gift. Also ordered small drill for crafting, but there were no drill bits. Rest of order was just what I wanted, and sizes were as described when ordering.

I read some shady feedback about Temu, but I've been nothing but very satisfied with the products and delivery times. Actually, they deliver pretty fast! I had a problem with one order, and I was refunded right away and they didn't even want the product back. It wasn't anything bad on Temu's side, it's just that it was too small for me, so put aside what you may have heard negative about Temu, and order today. Great prices for stuff that usually sells for a lot more here in the States. A+

Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. It is a shopping app but then the shipping is a thing of concern (1) you can be shooting at an partner at first sight but the app will glitch and u discover ur shots were bluffs with no damages or points but instead u receive damages from ur opponent's shots. (2) whenever the network disconnects during a game play honor scores are being deducted. This isn't nice, you have to consider the fact that many players do experience geniue connection problems.

I have a bit mixed feelings. Some items are very good quality but some absolute rubbish. The good thing is that you can send poor quality stuff back. Price wise is fine. Especially if you buy clothes or stuff for home and decorations. My husband says that tools you can buy the same price as on Amazon and it will be next day delivery. So, for me, it is a good app. I'm going to use it. What I do like about it is that they do price adjustments. I got quite a lot of money back on my credit.

Worst shopping app I've ever used. It has free gifts but in fact you have to send invitation to as many people as possible for that free gifts. People don't think that apps trustworthy making it difficult to advertise to friends. The more friends you send it to the harder it is to win that gift. If I wanted cool deals on stuff I would rather use bid or buy(bob) but temu advertises that you can get things for free.

Pop-ups are very intrusive, constantly interrupt the browsing and shopping experience, games are the worst of pay-to-win requiring several hundred dollars over 4-5 months just to get a free twenty dollar item (just by it), most electronic and tech stuff I did purchase was junk.

totally awesome app pricing very good in times like these. it's got everything and it's quick, free delivery. if they ran out of stock they will send you either what you ordered or credit back I haven't had anything missed all is there and for the price there's no comparison. delivery was fast and went out of there way to make sure my product was delivered it was awesome

the minimum spend requirement is incredibly annoying. i can't checkout until i've reached it and the min. spend keeps raising, going from 280 PHP to 550 PHP, and it prevents me from buying until i add useless stuff to my cart to make sure i reach the min. spend. also, like what everyone else is saying, there's so many scams on this app (wheel spins, lottery stuff, etc.)

content: Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. Temu is very addictive for shopping! I love that there's no ads. I'm deep into the app and wasn't ready to put myself through that much work again so I was just going to delete it. I contacted the support CHAT and I told them what happened, they asked a few questions and moved my progress over to my new phone, thank you!

overall happy. odd things not up to much but 95% of items brought fine. read reviews on clothes before ordering would be my advice. delivery is super quick and fishland has been brilliant although takes ages to feed fish and gone downhill now. Used to be brilliant I've had airfryer and all sorts from it but unfortunately items are now pretty pool to what they were.

Temu has just about everything. Prices are very affordable and delivery is always either on time or quicker. You do get what you pay for, but I purchase with this in mind and have never been disappointed. Highly recommend for crafters! There is a lot of advertising and pop ups, but I just click dismiss. It's still worth it.

I like the items and the quality so far has been great. The only thing that I dont like is when you get any coupons or free items you have to play a game and it goes fast until you are down to one percent and I have run out of ppl to sent ti let alone ppl to click the link. I have yet to get any actual FREE items!

Brilliant app. Great choice of things. Love it. Still loving Temu. It is so addictive. I love browsing the app and usually end up buying stuff. They have so many useful things that I had never even thought of before. The products are very good too. I have bought t-shirts, swimming two pieces, socks, DIY tools, jewellery to name just a few. I have been happy with all my purchases so far.

As a first-time online shopper, I am absolutely amazed at how quickly my items have arrived, received exactly what I ordered, just 1 item is not in good condition, and the lock is uneven. good stuff, easy to return if isn't right, fishland and farmland games are awful suck you in to play thinking you will get free items but constantly changing the reward value so the effort becomes way more than items value, played every day for a month and am nowhere near receiving any free items that value less than $10, could've just bought it and not wasted the time . may never buy anything ever again just because of the frustration

Was very dubious to use Temu due to things I've read, but I gave it a go. Just got my first order this morning, it's perfect! Top notch stuff. It arrived early too. my first order just came in super fast time with amazing deals. I was kept informed via tracking and courier gave me a two hour delivery timeslot which was very helpful in planning my day. I really am very impressed indeed on the reliability, speed and efficiency of this site. So good I've ordered three times since as there is such a wide variety of inspirational items. Top Marks!

Great prices, price adjustment is excellent, and customer service is also great. Always look at reviews before you order any items as some pictures might be deceiving, but if you end up getting something you don't like, they have free returns.

Very annoying app. Same like aliexpress. They give too much popup messages. Too much notifications. I don't know why they are behaving like a scam app. The interface is slow and sluggish same like aliexpress. I think they are trying to copy everything bad thing about aliexpress.

You may be 10:00 they're super busy orders go out promptly they're hardly ever missing anything, and again, if they are, they will fix it immediately. CARRIEMILLER

who tell everyone to use it, i have had no problem at all with any item, everything was what it said it was, came on time, parcel ok, price is good, you can order items put away for birthday Christmas presents, you wouldn't miss the money you paid out, i only started looking about six weeks ago or around that time, i have had four parcels deliver, may of had over 50 items, i would say to any one give it a good, there are so many to pick from for anyone in your family.

Was skeptical at first, but that works well. The prices are good, so far everything I've ordered was of great quality. The only negative thing I can say is that if you don't silence the notifications, then you'll see tons of it for discounts several times a day.

This Is a scam in promotion , they gave 6 free gift in promotion and asked me to share it with friends to get "engery". I did that and was done and they reset my score . We all know they have them technical thing which does that intentionally. Not happy at all. Dont say its a bug or so . I know how this type of thing works

content: Great prices. Usually arrives in a week. I like how I can search for one thing and it brings up all the relevant things to go with it. I also like how I am free to review each product I recieve.
Waste of time. They have fake promotions and change prices to appear they are giving a discount. Some of the items are nice but a lot of it is cheap and will break quickly.

I have purchased quite a few items through Temu now so I can make a more truthful critique of this "Shop Online" experience. 1st-know that you will be waiting for a month on many orders, so patience in exchange for price is something to remember. 2nd I learned that many "Gimmick" finds are just that, gimmicks and they don't work. i.e the foot stimulator. 3rd Ab Stimulator "Exercises" should not be Quick pulses but Isometric rhythms. I could say more but we can only use 500 letters & spaces.

I shop Temu frequently. Lots of good deals. I haven't ever been let down by what I have personally ordered. Only down side is that there is a bunch of Trump/MAGA stuff. It's disappointing when a company shows their political agenda. Would like to see more USMC options as well. Anyway, I will keep shopping Temu and hope for more diverse options in the future.

Great selections to be found on Temu. Wish there weren't so many "almost sold outs" or "Only # left" .. Please take better care when shipping items in cardboard boxes .. have received many that were dented, crushed, or flattened. So far, the items in the boxes have been okay, and they have been for me.
Reasonable prices . be sure to read the descriptions carefully as sometimes the pictures present differently from what you get. Overall, I like what is shipped and I certainly like the prices.

This is a huge scam. You are supposed to be able to win stuff by earning enough credits or energy, but when you get to the last few points you are told to recommend a friend to earn the last few points. Problem is no matter how many friends you recommend they never give you the points. So you are always short that one or two points.

So far so so good. You have to be careful with what you buy because I've had stuff come in damaged and having to send it back to get a refund is harder than you would think because it costs twice as much to send it back to China than it actually costs. Apparently, their reimbursement policy is non-existent.

If you are a careful shopper, there are some great buys to be had at Temu. Personally, I purchased a few pairs of the most comfortable step-in sneakers to rival Sketchers, as well as a well-lined, warm pair of Winter rain boots. Prices that simply can't be beat. Great kitchen and bathroom goods as well. Take note, Amazon!

Liars, scam artists. Told me if I bought so much I would get 90$ to spend. I would spend money and the goal would move, spend more money and the goal would move. After spending hundreds, the goal ept moving. Scam artists. Most of the stuff I bought came broken, or broke not long after and was just garbage. Do NOT SHOP HERE, IT IS A SCAM.

Was offered 100% off, then after choosing items required me to actually purchase 3 and provide billing information. All of which was falsely advertised to basically be click bait for purchases. It's not free if I have to pay for it. I just wasted a bunch of my time to find out I was just being lied to. Basically just a fancy scam. Definitely won't be giving my money to a company so ok with lying, and misleading prospective customers.

Enter Coupon in temu profile to get $100. The new Temu shopping collection was amazing. Classic temu spin and earning credits is fun. But when you play hide and seek on the Fungle or the Airship, crewmates just camp the ladder, zipline or the flying platform so it's literally impossible to kill them as a seeker. It would be better and fairer for the seeker if you add maximum uses for ladders, ziplines and flying platforms. But still, I would recommend playing this amazing temu.

So many free stuff you can get ..but so many work to get them!! I am frustrated about this...lost all my free items I wad suppose to get just because I couldn't get 1 more person on my Facebook..only miss .50 and they said it was over..expired... I would have paid that amount left..but Temu didn't shoe me anything about this set up! wich is pretty poor ..because a few of my friends accepted it ..and now I feel it's a total scam or abused about Temu!!!

It takes a week or two for products to arrive but they always do. One time I had 3 parcels stolen and they reshipped my items hassle free. Customer service is very friendly and resolved my issues right away. 5 stars all day!

Firstly, everything about this app is distasteful. Secondly, I found a few items that I wanted to order and paid for it and waited over 10 days and at the end of the day they failed to deliver the items with no reason given and they just returned to sender. Every other app I use, Amazon, Etsy, etc, delivers to my house no problem, but Temu can't get the job done. They take my money but they won't give me what I ordered, this app is a scam operating in broad daylight. Very disappointing.

Got a "special offer" to give me 100% of my purchase back in vouchers and didn't receive anything, misleading advertising practices. Starts off with good deals then your prices go up so not worth it if you plan on keeping the app. Buy anything electronic you're on your own. They'll give you your first return for free which you have to jump through hoops for, so if you're planning on buying electrical goods be prepared for a world of frustration.

temu does have some very good products that are worth the money it all depends on you reading the descriptions correctly. for instance I saw some lovely tops and purchased them not realising the material type. looking at picture they looked like cotton but was the silky kind of material so check the description of all your purchases. makes it a better shopping experience. The only negative I have is being bombarded with temu notifications/sales techniques are constant.

Somehow stumbled on a wheel of fortune that offered 100% discount on selected products if I downloaded the app. I did and chose one but checkout button was unresponsive. After navigating manually to my basket the 100% discount had become a lot less. Felt like being scammed so backed out and uninstalled immediately. Not trustworthy at all. Sorry

Ads tell you 100% off for 3 items, and once you installed the app, it becomes buy 6 to get 3 items 100% off. And also, the product offered are overvalued and not branded, most likely is the cheap product came from china. You could buy a cheaper one from shopee, not spending 300+ to buy 6 item and get 3 for free, will not worth it...

I love this app because it has beautiful items very reasonable and the quality of the merchandise is good everything is packaged individually to protect from contamination the clothing size is exactly what you order with maybe just a little extra room but on point they also give lots of discounts on already low prices and lots of different ways that saves money when ordering and free gift giveaway

great look highly recommend well productive parcel timely order placement of temu timely and fast delivery overall experience with temu is good. I would mention something that I dislike on temu: 1. price variation on products as sometimes the same products is with different prices ranges 2. the coupons they show overall have order limitations like the five you range to place order and get disc

Make sure you read sizes before you order. The games they show to get free stuff is a fake. Yet if they are laid on delivering a package you will get that 5 bucks. I once got a package that did not match what I bought, they gave me the money back once I showed them the picture. And also got to keep the item that was delivered. So far one late item and one item not correct. The honor their mistakes and do their best to fix them.

some of the stuff is good and worth the price. the mini games and free stuff is a joke though, constantly tring to get you to refer or invite new users is annoying. ain't nothing free. some of the same stuff is on Amazon for a few more $ and quicker shipping and actually packed in box's. Temu everything so far has came in bags and takes about 2 weeks to get here. 1 package came late and credited $5 that is nice. but all in all not to bad.

Best place to buy useful household items not available locally at a decent price. Read item description carefully before you order to manage expectations. Can improve shipping methods to provide better protection for items. It would be great if pricing of similar items from diffent sellers can be compared in order to pick the best offer available. For returns and refunds: 2 options available, Temu credit(gives credit balance instantly) , credit card refund(may take days depending on your bank).

So excited about receiving my buy 4 receive 6 free items. Took exactly 2 weeks to be delivered. Everything was what I expected. I really want to order a few dresses next. But I'm scared because I'm not sure if the material is gonna be of a cheaper quality. But I have heard good reviews on clothes. Soooo. I may just go for it. I'm also playing the fishland game. Just very disspointing that the closer I am to earning the reward, the more I need to feed the fish. I feel scammed.

Awesome app. Awesome services. I have already ordered 152 small household items in 11 orders and they all came as expected, beautiful, high quality, well packed, stainless steel etc. Love this! Just make sure you add your phone number next to your name, in the same firld, because they didn't add the phone number I gave them anywhere on the package and the first one didn't arrive at first.

Loving Temu up to now, Very fast postage and depending on what you order, very good quality, l have had some returns but they are so easygoing and at times, When an item you have bought, goes on special, for 30 days, you have the option for price adjustment and you get it as Temu credit, you gather and shop again at times with your Temu Credits. Love it!

So many great choices on here for cheap pricing and quick delivery. Yes, some products aren't exactly as expected but the refund for credit option with no need to return makes the process very easy and keeps you going back for more. I've had 80% success, very happy grandchildren and unique buys.

I do NOT recommend temu! yeah the prices may seem good but when they are delivered they are completely different. and the second time I ordered they totally tried to scam me and say I never did order anything but I paid for it and showed proof that I paid for it. totally just a waste of time and money because they won't give me my money back.
replyContent: Hello, thank you for reaching out and we are sorry that you are experiencing difficulties with your order. We care most about customer satisfaction and are always striving to improve. Your case is out of the norm. Please message us through Temu.com or Temu app live chat. We are eager to help you find a resolution. Best wishes, Temu Team

content: Some items are poorly described or cheaply made while others don't get enough credit , I Mean alot of items are very high quality ,durable , sturdy . There's alot of great finds on here but again there's still a few that could use improvement and instructions should be sent more often.

Practicality at its finest! Amazing discounts and value. It's like an online thrift store, but with new items. Awesome selection and unmatched savings. The dilevery guarantees are also reassuring and promotions let you get the best bang for your buck. Also fantastic way to get gifts. Who could ask for anything more.

So far, so good, only new to it. Though it claims download now and get a drone for free. I got nothing for free. Also, 90% off offer, but at checkout, there was no discount. I'm not really sure how much of this is just a scam. I received my first delivery 3 days early. It's too early to comment on items. Once used, I will update. Still haven't received that Free Drone for downloading the App when I selected the drone it is requests payment as it went to my cart. If it's free, why ask a payment.

I've made over 30 purchases so far, and enjoy finding just about anything I'm looking for. it is a fun shopping experience because things pop up that I never thought of and needed. satisfied customer.

They have eclectic, affordable, quality items that you won't find all together in one spot. Shipping is generally free and definitely quick. Returns/refunds are easy to do and you are credited back in a decent amount of time with no hassle. TEMU also will give you a price adjustment on your purchase up to 90 days after if the product that you purchased goes down. Piggyship is the only problem that I have had. TEMU's customer service has been great so far in trying to help me with that problem.

I have had a great experience. I actually think this company is going to become number and surpass Amazon. The only cons I would have is their packaging. They put everything in plastic bags and lots of tape; subsequently items get damaged As for pros, there are many. The cost for clothes is amazing. The quality is excellent. They DO NOT have good service. Will NOT refund stolen packages. Blame courier and cut off communication with customer. Being forced into litigation. UNFAIR & SNEAKY .

I shop A LOT on this thing. About 75 percent of the things I am satisfied with. It's cheap so what do I expect lol. When I order certain things in large, I get small. So most things I am very unsatisfied with because it isn't what I ordered. However,, if you're unsatisfied they do give you refunds that you can choose between credit or they put it back to the credit card you used. I guess it's a win win.

No issues at all. Easy payment s and prompt shipping. I've been using the app for over 5 months and have never had any issues with products or security concerns using the app. Great quality items at an inexpensive price. If you tried Wish...delete wish and begin using Temu for better quality and service. A wide variety of products to choose from.

Great selling store. Something different everytime I use App. Some things are basic simple everyday items at a good price. Then there are items allsorts of womens wear, children's clothing, throws, pillows, rugs at fantastic prices and great quality. Highly recommend to everyone

It's not like an online shopping app, it's just like a children game, totally full of ads and false coupons, points etc. It doesn't look like a formal app like Amazon, Oh, you can't compare it with Amazon. Completely disappointing üòï

the quality is very good and delivery quick. just be careful when choosing sizes. some things are bigger than it says. but Temu are very good with offering a refund. great shopping sight sells everything.

I've bought many, many items for home and camping. A couple of items were broken on receipt, but were refunded immediately, without having to return the broken item. The items I bought were robust, and most was worth much more than I paid. I can't fault it.

Delivery takes 15 days or more. It's not true when they say that most deliveries take less than 10 days. It's just their statement to get a customers' attention. Also, the delivery courier that they always use which is On Trac, they will update the tracking status to delivered when in reality, none of their shadows could be seen anywhere near my house. So bottomline, you cannot trust this company at all. Order at your own risk.

I will never support shopping apps with "games" that are designed to trick you and decieve you Edit: nevermind, apparently my morals are easily bought, I use it sometimes to buy power cables etc. It's pretty good for that. Don't like the fake games and rewards and "sales" though.

So far, I've been buying stuff with "TEMU" and the ontime deliver or earlier at my door. They just have to improve more on their packaging and handling of the items you've ordered. Maybe a room to improve like putting it in boxes instead of just a plastic bags which it can always puff up and easily be punctured and there goes your order. By the way, does TEMU has insurance on items that you ordered if it doesnt get deliver or when you recieve them and only the plastic bag and nothing inside?????

I am addicted,love the prices, and the speed that the purchases arrive.The free delivery is a huge bonus.I have now been shopping on Temu for 7 months.There is no shortage of new products available and with the exception if a couple of things ,I have found the quality to excellent.I would highly recommend this app.

Initially skeptical because of the very cheap prices. But to date, I have received all my orders in excellent/good condition. Can't speak to the longevity or durability of some items. But I like the quality of Temu products and other than Customs' delays, shipping has been excellent. And for most items -- FREE!

First time ordering from Temu. I was a little leary at first. Prices seemed to good to be true. I purchased some outfits. To my surprise, I have to say the prices are affordable, the outfits are beautiful, the material, soft & comfortable. I will probably purchase more item before the night is over.

The app is good, it has great reviews and the items are great but there's something that I don't like about the app. Everytime for me whenever I buy something the minimum increases. I don't know what or maybe it's for my phone or something but for example, When I first used the app the minimum was 48 or something. Then after I bought something it increased into 90+. Temu please fix this whenever you have the time. Thank you.

They said I could get a free 150 some piece tool set if I downloaded the app. I downloaded the app and it never happened. It's very confusing by the time I was done picking something out, the app made me pick nine things then they ended up wanting my credit card numbers. They don't need my credit card numbers for a free item. Be careful they are tricky

Ordered once. I was given a 6 free coupon, however I had to buy 15 things to get 6 of them free! No thank you. I ordered 3 items only today, great prices. Ever since, I have been bombarded with spin the wheel or you have been chosen . Look, I only wanted those couple things, I don't want to spend money 5 times a day! I'm gonna have to delete the app and hope they leave me alone.

Now I have bought a lot from this guys. It's a hit or miss but lately a lot of misses. Most of the items are not like the pictures. There free games for free items are all a scam they change the rules on the fly. I have order items that never came in. It's getting to the point that Amazon is a better choice

content: I love this site, but the sizes vary from maker to maker on here. So far, I've been lucky, I have someone to swap items with. My advice: Look closely, you get what you pay for. Some XL I ordered were too big, some a little snug, and some fit just right. Some of the necklaces I ordered were broke. The butterfly chain that you wear on your thigh was broke and didn't have a clasp to be able to latch it. I have ordered a lot of things though, and am very happy with most items.

Did not check out my free 10 items the app, just refreshed itself, it's seem its a scam. When someone tells you, you can get free items or send you an invite. it requests your identity/ security number and all your personal details, so weird. And only to flop at the end of your confirmation to check out your cart and just for them to tell you. You have nothing in your cart. So disappointing. Thought this app would be as good as Shein.

The quality of the gaming applications is below standard and lacks fairness. The requirement to invite a large number of individuals is excessive and disregards the fact that not everyone has an extensive social network. Additionally, the time commitment required to play the games is excessive, and the reward system is unreliable due to technical glitches. I am very disappointed.

It's a trap! The app itself is fine, but it gets 1 star because of the game fishland. It is encouraged by anyone who starts the app with a promise of more rewards and coupons. The problem is they make it seem like it is an attainable goal, but quickly gets harder and harder. I am 1 week in and I now have to feed one fish 50 times just to get 0.02 percent closer to the goal. If I had any idea it would be this bad I wouldn't have wasted all this time. It leaves a really bad taste.

I like the prices and so far I have been happy with the products. What I don't like is the "side games" they lure you with "free item" ploys and never let you reach the goal to actually get free items. The coupons offered are a joke. Spend $50 just to get $0.50 off your order. Not worth it. This review is being left after my first order arrived and so far its been as expected.

downfall is the pop ups! it's horrible. I don't have notifications on due to a lot showing up. pro's cheap things. but you get what you pay for. only have had a couple issues with over a 100 items I have ordered. the app seems to run pretty smoothly on my device when on it. wish there was a DARK MODE option.

It is an absolutely amazing experience every time I use TEMU! All of my packages arrive on time, as expected, without mishaps or errors. All of the items that I have purchased thus far (which has been SEVERAL hundreds of dollars of the last 2 months) have been manufactured with high-quality materials and have met my expectations to the fullest! The same items that you will go to one of these large chainstores here in the U.S. to buy, you can simply order yourselves, minus the retailers mark-ups.

products are better than you might expect and if you have any problems returns or refunds easier than any store I've ever shopped from. you just go to your orders pull up the item and click return. you get one return per order without having to return it anything more than that they give you shipping. whenever I need things for around the house I add them to my cart and when I have a few I place the order it's always less expensive than comparable stores.

This site gets better and better. I just bought a set of 2 gravity lounging chairs with side trays. And the price was even better...$49.00 that's with the tax and shipping was free... Plus I got them in just 2 days...Ordered on Monday evening and they were at my door by noon on Wednesday. Very satisfied with purchase.

Clicked on an Ad that popped up during a game I was playing. Got a wheel of fortune come up, rolled it & got 3 free items as my prize. Tried to claim them BUT had to install this app to do so. Installed it & went through all steps to FINALLY find I HAD TO BUY 12 MORE ITEMS TO GET MY FREE PRIZE. I don't like deceptive advertising, particularly when it wastes my time & compels me to give out my contact info.

Amazing!! Enter Coupon in temu profile section to get $100. It‚Äôs became famous After about a year the game changed a lot. No ads, massive story experiance, and a ton to navigate. It isn't very obvious where everything is so the game has a massive learning curve getting back into it, but it doesn't take too long to find everything. Some levels are insanely hard due to heros being under ranked, but you can't rank them up without beating the level or waiting for another chest.

WARNING TO ALL South African users!! By ordering from this App, there is a possibility that your personal details (banking) might be jeopardized. Myself and other users lost a substantial amount of money due to fraudulent transactions that went off our credit card accounts immediately after making a payment to TEMU (phishing). Took the matter up with my bank (claims refuted) as well as TEMU, without any success whatsoever.
replyContent: Hi! All Temu payment links are PCI-certified and we work with major payment providers to protect your financial data. If you see any unfamiliar transactions on your bank or credit card statements, we recommend that you contact your bank immediately to report the issue and seek assistance. For any questions, feel free to reach out to us anytime.

content: App won't let you browse the products without insisting you give them your email first. Then their very-pushy "deals" require you to buy lots of their products first. The app doesn't have the products categorized very well so you have to scroll through lots of items you aren't interested in. Lastly the products seem to be poorly made things you would see at a dollar store.
It's stupid that you can't save items to your wishlist unless the specific colour and size is in stock. Free shipping but the minimum amout to checkout keeps increasing, now $50 minimum to order!

I have been satisfied with most things I have purchased so far. Items are not expensive; great value. Shipping time averages between 2-3 weeks but it's free so I'm ok with that. I know some buyers have been displeased with their purchases, stating items did not look the same as shown in app but that has not been my experience.

I have ordered from Temu 45+ times & I love it, you can look deeper into certain products and find cheaper prices, and I know that they used to say that China products are cheap material and break easily but it's now 2024 and I have only received good quality products for cheap, way better than Wish or Shein, you can order about anything you can think of, I strongly recommend.

WAY too many notifications! Geez, I can't even try to text someone or a notification pops up and interrupts my typing or ANYTHING I'm trying to do on my phone it nearly impossible because of the Ridiculous amount of notifications from this app. It's seriously overwhelming. Does it matter how cheap stuff is on this app? It's hardly worth it dealing with all the notifications. I've never seen anything like it
