content: The app is very... Predatory The app will effectively give you fake coupons nonstop that say 70-90% off products, which is just a blatant lie as the producta shown are marked up 70-90% so instead of getting a discounted product you're paying full price or sometimes higher. Furthermore, it will tease you with "free" products that are only obtained through spending large amounts of money on other products. Also, don't give them permission for notifications, they will spam you.

Sometimes get caught up looking at the myriad of products.. I can. Spend at least a 1/2 an hour. Looking at everything that's available. And I'm tempted each time to buy a 1/2 a dozen things.. It's not only good stuff already bought. But many more that I would like to buy. Have turned temu on to several friends who have also Begun to enjoy the shopping.

Horrible usage quality, theres an invite friends get free gift thing and it requires you to invite like 20 people to get the free stuff, very rigged, cant even pick the things with search bar cause its useless it will only show up products with low prices and not what you want even though it actually exist on the platform and are very easy to find with no "free deals" on, ridiculous amount of time to finish app also very bad UI, make you go insane with ads. 1 star!

I feel like I should get some sort of receipt showing what my purchases are. When I don't receive a package. I can't figure out order and pkg. Status. OccSionally Message passes by saying I received a $5credit? I have to watch my card caregilly. Hadst $500purchase. What was it and where is it. Justbe careful. Their website is tricky and phishing I think.

Always have had a good buying experience. Not hard to get a refund or help with any questions, but I've had so many great experiences with good quality merchandise myself. TEMU has a huge variety of items, lightening and clearance sales, as well as new items that come in often. Be sure that you check the size of what you're buying. You can see sizes when you click on the item picture. There are fun games to play for free prizes, coupons and money!

my go to shop for all my essential needs, & wants as well. everything is perfectly priced, and I can find almost anything and everything I'm looking for at other stores for 1/2 the price here. u can't beat their daily deals and promotions they do as well. highly recommend this store for your every day needs!

I was able to place items before to my cart, have them shipped and delivered, but now every items that I clicked could not be added to my cart saying that "it can't be shipped to my default address " which I find weird because I had used the same address on my previous orders without any problems

They do save you money, but Dam do they bug you. Its hard to get them to stop. With buy this and save that like you need to buy something every hour of everyday. They there pictures do match what you get. There free things are not. FREE you have to spend $100.00 or more to get. Like the games that say they give free money but when comes to paying you, you need to spend more then they are giving you.

Excellent products. Everything purchased was exactly as advertised. One of the many items that I purchased was slightly damaged during shipping, and I received a full refund without a hassle. Originally, I couldn't believe their prices, but not only are the prices legit, but so are the quality of the items that Temu are selling. Never pay retail again. Also, you can't beat the free guaranteed shipping. I am now a lifetime shopper. I have passed the word throughout my friends and family.

It's not too bad with their prices, the shipping is fairly quick. The hats that I buy, usually are squashed beyond fixing, the other thing is make sure you look at the sizes of everything. I purchased some make-up sponges, they were that small that I couldn't hold onto them. If something is wrong with any of their products, don't hesitate to contact them.

It's a great app for getting cheaper prices on stuff, but I can't stand all the pushy ad's...and I would not recommend playing the games for "free stuff" it's not free stuff if you have to drive your family and friends crazy with all the invite messages and the constant pushing to buy more stuff...after I played the games for over a month, I quit because it was becoming more difficult to get what you need...

content: Despite what is said about whatever information is taken from us, every app does it. I know not every item is exactly what you expect, but I've enjoyed almost every item I've purchased. They arrive quicker than SHEIN or WISH and the prices are great for the most part. The only thing I'm not huge on is the fact that they ask for more and more purchases in order to gain points or coins even with a membership.

It is a great store to purchase items from. You can get great items at a very discounted price!!!? Well worth your time. I have been using them for over a year I believe and have never had any problems with there items. If I purchase something I really don't like I can return it with no questions asked and can get all money reimbursed. Good Company!!!

I enjoy shopping with Temu for household, clothing, linens, gadgets and so much more. I find the prices just right, styles are so cute and there's so much to choose from. Shipping is free and returns are sooo easy.

Prices are low because the goods are cheap. The pictures of what you see advertised may not be what you actually get. Temu is a Communist China-based app and site. As you shop, Temu monitors your activity on other apps, tracks your notifications and location and changes settings. Temu gains full access to all your contacts, calendars and photo albums, plus all your social media accounts, chats and texts. In other words, literally everything on your phone
replyContent: Hi! At Temu, we prioritize the protection of privacy and are transparent about our data practices. We collect information with a clear and singular purpose: to provide and continually enhance our products and services for our users. The data we gather reflects common industry practice. Their clothing is great, unique, and true to size. Their toys were a bit of a disappointment. They were mostly cheap, easily destructible and smaller than the pictures. Household stuff for great prices. I love the variety on this app.

great app for bargain shopping... and the little side games (feeding fish in a virtual aquarium for extra bonus) can be ignored if one doesn't want to bother. I was sceptical at first and did a test buy, with great discount as a first time shopper and I was so surprized with the quality of most things I ordered, I've been ordering many times since... delivery is usually around 10 days and the sizes of the clothes are actually true to size.

Good site to shop. Keep me up-to-date with tracking, even have a direct link to Auspost. I've had a discount for parcel being a couple of days late, a refund for one that was lost but got delivered anyway, and a refund for an item I mistakenly bought, all with no hassles. Very transparent good customer service. You can tell they're customer oriented now.

Its a good app, and the price is cheap... But the problem is they are giving coupon with minimum order , they can give coupon without minimum order, and the when you are about to get the prices the points they are giving become less and less so you can't finish it...

TEMU has good prices and good quality of items, I haven't had many problems anything I've ordered. I also have had super fast delivery times. I will be buying from them quite often. The only thing I don't like is having to invite others to play the games all the time. I have been trying to win some prizes for a week now and still can't get them.

Got over loss of wishlist. Many purchases. Lots of plusses shopping TEMU: free shipping, lots of exclusive offers, games with free prizes, and the guarantee of quality a big plus. Wish they would use boxes for delivery. Would pay more for boxes.

My only complaint is that I spend too much money. Their free games and prizes appear to be scams, while you will get your absolute cheapest item at times only, you will. never be able to reduce the price by the final penny. This has been the case for myself and everyone I know.

I have ordered over a thousand dollars worth of purchases and have only had one item coming cracked, a wooden spoon. I could not be happier with everything I have purchased! I have not been more pleased by the purchases.I have made especially items for my daughter's wedding. The clothes are fantastic and true to size. I have encouraged so many others to start purchasing as well!

Just getting worse with every shopping. Minimum purchase amount increasing by 5‚Ç¨ with every purchase, used to be minimum 10‚Ç¨ then 15,20 and now minimum purchase is 25‚Ç¨, that is ridiculous and very cheap trick. Bombarded with tons of messages with fake offers and discounts, prices are getting higher as well. Not worth it, unsubscribe.

Am just using my mom's account for this. but this app is so annoying due to that amount of ads and fake skinny wheel stuff because if u think ur getting a discount off u aren't. there is so much pop up ads to the point weren't not even touching the phone and gives a pop up ad. u can't search up anything at all without being disturbed by an ad. it's honestly a shifty app with OK qualities clothing. and I would love to give a zero but sadly I can't

Really great design . There is know metal arm. So they are very flexable. They are the best performing wipers i have ever purchased. And very cheap price. You will be completly satisfied. I love this new design. Im a master tech with ford motor company. So i have a little knowledge on the subject. Trust me great wipers. Amazing price. I would stake my life on the quality and price.

Honestly, I was skeptical of using Temu due to some reviews and articles in the news media. Then my co-workers were raving on their Temu items, the prices and great customer service &after seeing the great quality items in person I decided to take the plunge. I'm so glad I did! I'm getting done great items very cheap, they are true to their delivery times & excellent at providing tracking. I do not at all feel like my privacy or data is breached, my items are packaged well. Thank you Temu! ü•∞‚ù§Ô∏è

Sometimes you don't receive the item that you thought you were ordering. But that has been rare with my orders. I am 95% happy with my purchases. I love the discounts and Free Shipping. You can even request a refund without a hassle. I recommend shopping this Website if you love bargains and saving money.

Have to send some items back as (probably packer) having a bad day and just dumping what came to hand. (very occasionally) VERY addictive because of the pricesüòÅ ALL in all, quite happy with what I've ordered. Notifications on delivery time, very good, prices are great, (Clothes, I've learnt, you'll have to order a size up) Quite happy with the service (apart from having to wait for deliveries!) üòÅ

Confusing, time crunch push for sales in minutes. Totally different prices in shopping basked then what you had in offer, cannot check items in basket before ordering in "action". Change of price between basket and payment screen. You choose item in action for lets say 20czk in basket when goes to payment it change to 150czk. Honestly it looks more like scam than serious "shop". After while you get noy requested spam and scamming messages about winning etc. Do not install or use at all.
replyContent: Hello, thank you for reaching out and we apologize for any inconvenience. We care most about customer satisfaction and are always striving to improve. Your case is out of the norm. Please message us through Temu.com or Temu app live chat. We are eager to help you find a resolution. Best wishes, Temu Team

content: Temu drags you along. They send you all these good deal's but when get close to achieving it they dragged it on by having you buy more and more stuff before they give you the great deal. It seems like nothing but a scam. And as far as fishland their game you're only 5% away from getting it all free and again they'll never let you get there. I would recommend that some of those go through. There's got to be a winner at some point.

If I accidentally click on it while doing something else, i can't just back out Ihave to close everything to get out of the app. I have had good luck with all my purchases so far with th exception of the silver chains I purchaced. The silver wore off. üòè

Constant spam and promotions with hidden agendas. Every single notification that you're going to get multiple times per day is aimed at getting you to open the app and purchase from a variety of useless junk Chinese gadgets. Delete this garbage from your phone, or never install it in the first place.

Great shopping experience. As with any shopping app there are hang ups but temu resolves their issues with the customer in mind transactions with care and prompt resolve so the customers confidence is restored one way or another. It's a win, win for both customer and retailer. THANKS AGAIN!!

Just placed my first 3 orders, so not sure what to expect, ut according to friends, its pretty good cheap prices, so will update this once the items have been recieved. However one star is lost because there should be a WISH LIST to add to, so then I can order it when ready instead of looking for the item all over again.

good service for cheap goods. mostly no issues at all. just watch out for some "deals". they have one like 100% rebate on orders up to $50. but nah they just give a coupon like 30 off 70, which expires quickly. still good but be aware.

Originally, I gave Temu 5 stars because the prices were unbeatable. Yes, shipping did take a few weeks but it was usually less than 2, which is completely acceptable. However, as it got more popular I saw prices rise and the CEO's pockets swelling up; the prices are no longer anything special and in fact, they are bad and expensive for products that are passable at best. Horrible place to shop.

Interface is annoying, makes you sit through like five cheap looking animation before telling you none of those deals apply unless you buy 7 more items. The products have been decent quality, about what I'd expect to find in a Dollar General I'd say.

Amazing deals, but watch out for the NEVER ENDING GAMES they just string you along, trying to get you to invite more people to spread the word about them. But the prices are amazing, and the shipping is under 2 weeks for delivery, and most of the time, free shipping. Just get past the tempting, Neverending Free Products, games

I give it 3 star. It's really cheap, but you have to get up to 10 pounds yo actually buy something, and if u know me, it's REALLY cheap, so 10 pounds is like a million pounds And I don't like where u have to go to the cart to checkout like... but I hope the new update is good. The app is really cheap and good but I wanna checkout while buying NOT IN THE CART

Love the app. Easy to get refunds. That said, be very, very careful about what you're buying. Clothes may be smaller than US sizes, many clothes you think will be stretchy are not. The clothes are usually very well made and wear well, including washing and drying very well. A lot of the products may be innovative, but are junk that falls apart. Read descriptions thoroughly! You won't be wasting $ if you are careful. Keep in mind where the products originate.

Data leak, had fraudulent phishing attempts within hours of me placing an order with this app, I get texts informing me to pay customs when the order hadn't even been picked and shipped yet. Now I get bombarded with texts asking for payment, hard to decipher the real ones from fake ones. Rather use shein, they're faster, been using it for well over a year and never got any phishing attempts.
replyContent: Hi! At Temu, we prioritize the protection of privacy and are transparent about our data practices. We collect information with a clear and singular purpose: to provide and continually enhance our products and services for our users. The data we gather reflects common industry practice. For further information, please refer to our privacy policy.
